Subject: Body Painting
Description: Come watch a live demonstration of body painting!  Jeannie Arquette and her team from Artifice FX will create a character design just from body paint on a model while you watch! This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:Jeannie Arquette, Maurianna Reid, Estaria Arquette - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes
